text: Olga Göllner (born 8 November 1930) is a Romanian gymnast. She competed in seven events at the 1952 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1930 births Category:Living people Category:Romanian female artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Romania Category:Gymnasts at the 1952 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Cluj-Napoca
